  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A hot &amp; cold breakfast buffet is served each morning in the indoor dining room and on the outdoor terrace in warmer months. You'll have all you need to kick start a day of exploring the local area.</p>
<p><strong>La Veranda </strong>restaurant offers a more casual setting with some of the best aperitivi on the lake. The restaurant is open for breakfast, a snack lunch and serves a delicious a la carte dinner (bookable &amp; payable locally). It's the perfect location to sit and watch the world go by.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
