  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Grand Hotel Menaggio has the best location in town. It's right next to the lake and in front of the ferry port so it couldn't be easier to get out for the day to explore <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a>. It has a real old-world charm - the building is palatial and stands out beautifully on the lakefront.</p>]]></listingDescription>
